<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hitherto" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hitherto,</orth> 1) to this place: <cit><quote>England, from Trent and Severn h.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.1.74" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 1, 74</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) to this limit, so far: <cit><quote>and h. doth love on fortune tend,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.216" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 2, 216</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I am h. your daughter,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 1.3.185" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 3, 185</bibl></cit>.
<lb />3) to this time: <bibl n="shak. h5 5.2.15" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V, 2, 15</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.3.9" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 3, 9</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.2.1" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C IV, 2, 1</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.1.82" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 1, 82</bibl> (Qq <emph>ever since</emph>). <bibl n="shak. h8 5.3.32" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 3, 32</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.2.247" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 2, 247</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>